name: daily dose of knowledge
description:
Issue 06/?
DEMONS Magazine

_

It's not your blood what I want.
I want your ideas, your thoughts
I want to make them forever mine, 
all of your mind, that's what I brought.

I'm going to be what you always were,
saying the words you always said,
and the ones you never could before.

I will be loved by the ones who once loved you,
and the ones who loved me before.
What could be better than to have you?
Inside my mind, and forever more.
